nodes.text: This individual worked as a bounty hunter sometime before 0 BBY. They were successful at their trade, and as a result were able to afford high-quality weapons. They owned a set of Mandalorian armor and also owned an astromech droid, modified with two droid brains. They died when their starship crashed into Tatooine's Western Dune Sea, with the wreckage being discovered and looted by a tribe of Jawas. One of the Jawas, Jot, took possession of what was left of the hunter's droid.
